{
  "text": "In order to establish a highly efficient, leak-proof and tamper-proof key extraction mechanism in a WSN [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , physical unclonable function (PUF) [CITATION_3] has been proposed in recent years. Due to the differences of manufacturing, PUF can be considered as an electronic fingerprint for which the",
